DESCRIPTION:Next meetup on November 30 2022 in Otaniemi at 15:00. The room 
 is TBA. This will be the\nfirst of a "library development" series\, where 
 we will gradually develop a library together\nand add features step by 
 step. During the first meeting\, we will have a general overview\nof a 
 Julia library structure and general development workflow. As always\, free
  of charge\nand refreshment included. If you are coming\, please register 
 by Thursday 24th November.\nSee https://julia-users-helsinki.github.io/ 
 for details.\nlocation: TBA
